    "## 2. Data Acquisition and Preprocessing\n",
    "We need to load 19 separate files. To keep the code efficient, we will:\n",
    "1.  Identify files for **Sale** and **Rent** separately.\n",
    "2.  Extract the **Year** and **Month** from the filename to create time-series features.\n",
    "3.  Combine them into two master DataFrames: `df_sales` and `df_rent`."
